{"tid":1976500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"呂智恆：入稟為拆穿林鄭擋箭牌","createTime":"2020-04-17T09:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T14:36:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"84edf19e82aeb42546314b31bfc427c9b5fd6124","tid":1976500,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200417/AH3EL23FW5CBGK5YYTT2DLUSIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2FAH3EL23FW5CBGK5YYTT2DLUSIA%2F&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9yq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=170aa004\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2FAH3EL23FW5CBGK5YYTT2DLUSIA%2F&h=29af9830\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200417/AH3EL23FW5CBGK5YYTT2DLUSIA/</a><br />\n<br />\n呂智恆：入稟為拆穿林鄭擋箭牌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200417/large/1587055026_a684.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200417%2Flarge%2F1587055026_a684.jpg&h=6cc4d606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n申請人呂智恆（中）昨指希望上訴，但要與律師團隊商討才決定。楊思雅攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥一直拒回應社會就獨立調查反送中的訴求，多次推搪須待監警會報告出爐後才回應，一拖便十個月。呂智恆昨強調，入稟只為拆穿林鄭拒獨立調查的擋箭牌，指監警會無權傳召證人，絕不接納其所謂查找事實的報告。他更一度哽咽指：「（手足）流咗咁多血，我哋要獨立調查委員會，唔係監警會作古仔。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：法庭裁審視反送中無越權 監警會報告最快下月出爐<br />\n<br />\n稱報告公開亦不應接受<br />\n<br />\n呂智恆昨親自到法庭領取判詞，向對判決有期待的手足表示抱歉。他坦言，個人立場而言，非常希望上訴，但是仍然要與律師團隊商討判詞，才可以作進一步的決定。<br />\n<br />\n對於有聲音質疑，既然獨立調查未有聲氣，是否應先擱置法律訴訟，公開監警會的報告？呂反駁指監警會報告公開與否，市民皆不應接受，並指監警會過去多年均是以正常投訴程序辦事，跟進和審視投訴警察課的投訴個案，而非主動調查。他反問，若監警會有權主動調查，「點解16年嘅旺角衝突、14年嘅雨傘運動、12年嘅反國教運動，你唔去調查？究竟係你當時失職，定係𠵱家越權呢？」呂又質疑監警會的作用，為何過去十年只有三宗成功檢控的投訴個案。<br />\n<br />\n呂解釋，當日入稟司法覆核，是要拆穿林鄭月娥不成立獨立調查委員會的擋箭牌。他一度哽咽謂：「十個月喇，我哋一直堅持要獨立調查委員會。（手足）流咗咁多血，我哋係唔會接受監警會，一個所謂查找事實，但冇傳召證人權力組織所做嘅報告。」<br />\n<br />\n他重申五大訴求中除了實施雙普選外，其中最重要的一點，正是成立一個可以公平公正查出所有事情真相的調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n■記者楊思雅"},{"pid":"8b637a728408c91bea2949b9e441b915d6746195","tid":1976500,"uid":36877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c6e8ee156bd0bacbcb8ee58b9b072bf582728a","tid":1976500,"uid":24024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"新東人 投佢"},{"pid":"03b729a6ddbab0e21da018163e1ae7ad99eb2504","tid":1976500,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3X0Xdk7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3X0Xdk7.png&h=f37bd2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱見到<br />\n有無人幫幫佢"},{"pid":"b04c532f0730e20e20b2374e3c2db22288620c40","tid":1976500,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03b729a6ddbab0e21da018163e1ae7ad99eb2504","tid":1976500,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3X0Xdk7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3X0Xdk7.png&h=f37bd2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱見到<br />\n有無人幫幫佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}